          "clickHandlerArgs": {
            "title": "L-104 Cyber Security Lab",
            "description": "<h4>Purpose</h4><ul><li>Monitoring client's critical data and network activities</li><li>Detecting and responding to cybersecurity threats</li><li>Learning real-time security monitoring and incident response</li><li>Improving data protection and threat prevention techniques</li></ul><h4>Key Equipment</h4><ul><li>SIEM tools (Security Information and Event Management)</li><li>Firewalls and Intrusion Detection Systems (IDS/IPS)</li><li>Security monitoring dashboards</li><li>Threat intelligence and analysis tools</li><li>Secure servers and network monitoring systems</li></ul><h4>Skills Developed</h4><ul><li>Security threat detection and analysis</li><li>Incident response and mitigation</li><li>Network security monitoring</li><li>Cyber attack investigation</li><li>Data protection and risk management</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        {
          "pitch": 26,
          "yaw": 26,
          "type": "info",
          "text": "L-103 Cloud Computing Lab",
          "clickHandlerArgs": {
            "title": "L-103 Cloud Computing Lab",
            "description": "<h4>Purpose</h4><ul><li>Deploying and managing cloud-based infrastructure and services</li><li>Working with virtualization, containerization, and cloud orchestration</li><li>Learning IaaS, PaaS, and SaaS cloud service models</li><li>Building scalable and distributed applications on cloud platforms</li></ul><h4>Key Equipment</h4><ul><li>Cloud platforms – AWS, Microsoft Azure, and Google Cloud (GCP)</li><li>Virtualization tools – VMware, VirtualBox, and Hyper-V</li><li>Containerization – Docker and Kubernetes clusters</li><li>High-performance servers with multi-core processors and high RAM</li><li>Networking equipment for cloud simulation and SDN labs</li></ul><h4>Skills Developed</h4><ul><li>Cloud architecture design and deployment</li><li>DevOps practices – CI/CD pipelines, Infrastructure as Code</li><li>Containerization and microservices orchestration</li><li>Cloud security, identity management, and access control</li><li>Serverless computing and auto-scaling configurations</li></ul>"
          }
        }
